        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\n> I guess this may not be needed Alexis's commit https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/71369/ works out as it seems to be a better solution.\n\nMy fix is to make sure PVC are claiming PV that are created for them. I ended up in a case where an OOF PVC claimed an AAI PV.\nKubernetes will bbound any PV that has the claimed spec. Adding a matchLabel condition forces K8S to fullfill the condition to bound the PV.",
